- const {options} = htmlWebpackPlugin

section.contact#contact

	h2 ☎️ Contact

	p.status I am currently accepting new freelance projects.

	p The best way to get in touch with me is to email at <a href="mailto:mail@chaturvedi.dev">mail@chaturvedi.dev</a> or fill in the form below. <br> For a more informal tête-à-tête, you can contact me on <a href="https://t.me/plibither8">Telegram</a>.

	p Otherwise, you can connect with or follow me on any of the following networks too:

	.networks

		each network in options.networks

			a(href=network.link rel="noopener" target="_blank")
				img(
					src=network.icon
					alt=`${network.name} Logo`
					draggable="false"
				)
				| !{network.name}

	form(name="contact" method="POST" netlify)

		label(for="contact-form_name") Name
		input(name="name" type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" id="contact-form_name" required)

		label(for="contact-form_email") Email
		input(name="email" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" id="contact-form_email" required)

		label(for="contact-form_message") Message
		textarea(name="message" placeholder="Enter your message" id="contact-form_message" required)

		input(type="submit" value="Send")
